betterquesting.quest.xU7jtFxOQR-4ccpcXT3W2A.name=Паровая броня
betterquesting.quest.xU7jtFxOQR-4ccpcXT3W2A.desc=Ever wanted an power armor that is not using electricity power? Here it is, steam-powered power armor!%n%nSlows you down a little bit but gives you Haste V.


## Quest Line: Dimensional Adventures
betterquesting.questline.IvOaHFdvTem9AKGdPDgBaA.name=Путешествия сквозь измерения
betterquesting.questline.IvOaHFdvTem9AKGdPDgBaA.desc=Нет описания

# Quest: Void Quartz
betterquesting.quest.-WMTfvUrRlmEzH7hBIzMfg.name=Пустотный кварц
betterquesting.quest.-WMTfvUrRlmEzH7hBIzMfg.desc=Another type of quartz, called Void Quartz, can be found in the Abyss biome. It’s easy to spot thanks to the dark surroundings. Void Quartz is an essential material used in crafting advanced storage cells in AE2.

# Quest: Burning Stick
betterquesting.quest.2uw1IrVfTVKt_7dxdEsNOQ.name=Горящая палка
betterquesting.quest.2uw1IrVfTVKt_7dxdEsNOQ.desc=Ouch! Ouch! Hot!%n%nThe Blaze Rod is a vital material for reaching the End. It drops, of course, from Blazes — but be careful! They always spawn infernal, so prepare for a tough fight.

# Quest: The Nether
betterquesting.quest.DgW8bQi1TbSrKcPoJms-1g.name=Незер
betterquesting.quest.DgW8bQi1TbSrKcPoJms-1g.desc=§eThe Nether§r is home to many resourses, such as:%n%n§6Quartz§r§r which can be used for §6Silicon§r.%n§6Infernal Coal§r which can be shredded for §6Coal Powder§r.%n§6Sulfur§r needed for various chemical processes.%n§6Red Phosphorus§r for incendiary weaponry.%n§6Glowstone§r for early §bChlorine Gas§r in a §3Combination Oven§r.%n§6Cobalt§r can also be rarely found near the Nether Roof.%n%nThe Nether has a backround radiation of §e0.1RAD/s§r.§r%n%n§cYou will burn in Nether permanently.%n%n§2Glowstone, Quartz and Phosphorus Bedrock Ore Deposits also exist.§r%n%n§2Depth Neodymium Deposits also spawn exclusively in the Nether.§r %n

# Quest: Piglins?
betterquesting.quest.JfANYrzhQKCVY4ATmF-Tsg.name=Пиглинв?
betterquesting.quest.JfANYrzhQKCVY4ATmF-Tsg.desc=Hey, say hello to the piglins of 1.14! I think you know who they are.%n%nIf not, then listen up. Piglins are very similar to zombie pigmen, but they will be aggressive towards you if you don't have gold armor on you (that is, they will be aggressive towards you ALWAYS, because I don't know how you'll survive in hell wearing gold armor). Also, if you throw them a gold bar, they'll be willing to trade it for something else.

# Quest: Hellish Beauties
betterquesting.quest.LendIsa-Q2ugsj2GWM_D6Q.name=Адские красоты
betterquesting.quest.LendIsa-Q2ugsj2GWM_D6Q.desc=Crystals can be mined in the Crystal Biome. (Obviously.) They are mainly used to craft advanced Applied Energistics 2 storage cells, as well as some other less useful crafts, such as Crystal Lamps or Crystal Glasses.

# Quest: Crystal Clear Production
betterquesting.quest.XU2nsU1wQFG85rsSxuTPqA.name=Кристально чистое производство
betterquesting.quest.XU2nsU1wQFG85rsSxuTPqA.desc=You've already mined the Nether Crystals, but they can't be recrafted into Crystal Shards. Instead, all you need to do is pour water near the block — it will then transform into a Budding Nether Crystal. This structure will begin growing Crystal Buds in all directions, which will eventually develop into a Crystal Flower (the final stage). Once fully grown, you can safely break the flower to obtain the Shards needed for AE2.

# Quest: Efrine
betterquesting.quest.dsZj1Tv8Se6m5E8R2_e49Q.name=Эфрин
betterquesting.quest.dsZj1Tv8Se6m5E8R2_e49Q.desc=Stange material. Feels cold and soft, like plasticine. Anything made from this material does not burn, and the armor gives you fire resistance.

# Quest: Darkness in Powder Form
betterquesting.quest.rIM_8imCQdyHqdA2ih4brQ.name=Тьма в порошковой форме
betterquesting.quest.rIM_8imCQdyHqdA2ih4brQ.desc=An alternative to Glowstone can be found in the Nether, called Gloomstone. It generates in special biomes and is required for certain AE2 crafting recipes.

# Quest: New End
betterquesting.quest.vQm4mFhbRsS8yjm9DkDAUw.name=Новый Конец
betterquesting.quest.vQm4mFhbRsS8yjm9DkDAUw.desc=§eThe End§r is home to §6Trixite§r, a unique extraterrestrial mineral that when processed can yield §6Plutonium§r, §6Cobalt§r and §6Niobium§r. The Niobium is of great interest as it is a great source for early §3Catalytic Cracking Towers§r.%n%nDue to only the main end island existing, Trixite Ore is a limited resourse.§r Trixite Crystals can also be obtained from an §6Asteroid Mining Ship§r, but it is not recommended.%n%n§dEt Futurum Requiem§r backports many modern end features, such as §eChorus Fruit§r, §eShulkers§r and a respawnable §eEnder Dragon§r using §6End Crystals§r.%n%nThe §6Dragon Egg§r can also be used to create a Backpack which provides passive §eNight Vision§r, §eStrength 2§r and §eFire resistance§r, aswell as some §eRegeneration§r when on low health.%n%nEnderman farms can also be made using §3Fans§r to push the endermen into the killing zone.


